          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-666B34GJ-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">Y</hi>Ou've undone <hi rend="italics">Horace</hi>,--- what shou'd hinder</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666B34GJ-line-2" n="2">Thy muse from falling upon <hi rend="italics">Pindar</hi>?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666B34GJ-line-3" n="3">But e'er you mount his fiery steed,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666B34GJ-line-4" n="4">Beware, O <hi rend="italics">Bard</hi>, how you proceed:────</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666B34GJ-line-5" n="5">For shou'd you give him once the reins,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666B34GJ-line-6" n="6">High up in air he'll turn your Brains:────</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666B34GJ-line-7" n="7">And if you shou'd his fury check,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666B34GJ-line-8" n="8">'Tis ten to one he breaks your neck.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
